Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.43,B2,aRANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.59,B2,aRANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That’s odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.07,B2,aRANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Captain go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.64,B2,SQUAD MEMBER B,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re looking for \NCaptain Hitsugaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.22,B2,SQUAD MEMBER B,0000,0000,0000,,he’s supposed to be \Non leave starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:23.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That’s right. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.43,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,That means I’ll have to take \Ncare of all these documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:34.51,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, why’d you \Nhave to take leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.89,B2,DONI,0000,0000,0000,,Yours, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.17,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.22,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.90,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You sure saved us, Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.17,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,When Ryohei got hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.59,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,we didn’t know who we \Ncould get to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.83,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.36,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you be around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.13,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.66,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of answer is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:47.44,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how long are you going \Nto keep following me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.12,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m done helping your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.79,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.06,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.65,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.16,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It is you, Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.24,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.89,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I got to know Grandma Haru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.18,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,when I was stationed in \Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.57,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Stationed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.42,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t really get it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.36,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You were doing things like that \Neven though you’re a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.06,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, I’m not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:32.67,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru can see spirits \Nthe way you and Kurosaki can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.34,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.43,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder so many
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.33,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,of them are gathering in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:41.79,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:47.49,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Toshiro. It’s your \Nfavorite candied beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.68,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You like candied beans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.96,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You’re like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.69,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.02,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm… These are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.64,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:03.98,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming such a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:04.97,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.65,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it, Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.93,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to visit Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.65,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.54,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.78,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.65,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.28,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Were you there all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.78,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.33,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been staying \Nhere for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.71,B2,HITSUGAYA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Whole. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.34,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke, can you say \Nhello to our guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.00,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.69,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.20,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke is very shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.24,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,However, he’s the most visible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.69,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,wandering spirit since Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.20,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.71,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. You’re a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.23,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks to Yosuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.91,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m enjoying my life right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.85,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.92,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a family, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.88,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve lived alone all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.09,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.77,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:31.01,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, I have Yosuke \Nand many other spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:36.27,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes Toshiro comes to visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.98,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,so I’m not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.17,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,That’s great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.27,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,The wandering spirits that come
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.56,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,around me are all annoying ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.94,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,But Yosuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:49.28,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What is keeping you \Nfrom resting in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:54.96,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke wants to see snow. \NIsn’t that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.16,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.55,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke got into an accident \Nwhile he and his family
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.17,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,were on their way to go skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.24,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It was a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.55,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Many people lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.14,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,His parents seem to have \Npassed over in peace, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.12,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,this child was looking forward to \Nseeing snow for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:20.66,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That desire remained so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.42,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,that he was unable to rest in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.24,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,and I found him wandering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.92,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.90,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,But according to the weather forecast,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.68,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,it should snow soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.91,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:37.88,B2,YOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.53,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.48,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay…to leave \Nthat child like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:52.76,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.72,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.77,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t spirits that haven’t \Npassed over at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.32,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,If left alone…I don’t \Nreally understand this…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.65,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,but don’t they turn \Ninto like, monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.44,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.31,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,If he stays here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.91,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke will probably \Nturn into a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.34,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.46,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What you call a “monster.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.19,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Then won’t Grandma \NHaru be in danger too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.42,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.38,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It happened right about when \NI first became a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.87,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,I was dispatched before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.13,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,I knew what to expect from \Nthe World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.86,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,in order to gain experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.01,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,While I was stationed here, \NI simply followed orders
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.48,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,and spent every day \Ngetting rid of Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.11,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,Back then, all I thought about was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.56,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,getting rid of the \NHollows in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.18,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a fine sword you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:23.77,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,My, you’re such a tiny Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.34,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru had spiritual power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.28,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,and knew about Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:31.69,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,She looked after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.01,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you very clearly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.20,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in a gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.79,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,A gigai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.65,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a body for eating candied beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.46,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.72,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Then be sure to eat \Nlots before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:55.13,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,Grandma lost her family a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.76,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,and lived alone for all those years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.93,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,And, because she could see spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.39,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,everyone thought she was creepy \Nand kept their distance from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:09.82,B2,HITSUGAYA (N),0000,0000,0000,,Spirits were the only thing \Nthat eased her loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:15.67,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru thinks of \NYosuke like a grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.77,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.99,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to do \Nsomething for Yosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.11,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, I’d perform a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.88,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Konso as soon as I found \Na spirit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.10,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,But since I left him alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.14,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t allow this to \Ncause problems for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.00,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to watch over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.66,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You know, for a kid, \Nyou’re awfully caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.65,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Who’re you calling a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.50,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, you’ll be staying \Nhere a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.61,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have someplace to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.86,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.45,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Then come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.60,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.13,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Karin brought home a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.08,B2,KARIN /HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,-You’re wrong! \N-You’re wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.25,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,You two are perfect for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.93,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Aw jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.99,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the times for \NDad not to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.66,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.95,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:20.13,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, Toshiro will be staying \Nwith us a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.00,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.68,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Karin is becoming an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.81,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.81,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren’t you talking, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.64,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you friends with Toshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you \Nthink you’re doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.01,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.98,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.46,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,They won’t listen, no matter \Nhow much we try to correct them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.01,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:56.05,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu’s always like that, \Nso don’t let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You and Karin took it so seriously \Nthat I couldn’t help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t put Karin in danger, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.96,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.90,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going \Nto keep following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.31,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.17,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to \NGranny’s place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.15,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.82,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.75,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, you’ve come again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:32.72,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I took some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.05,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:38.71,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came with your \Ngirlfriend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.48,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.93,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,She’s not my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.01,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.48,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.48,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro’s here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.58,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:55.31,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a shy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.52,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:11:59.86,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:06.91,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.41,B2,YOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.88,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.95,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.17,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,My Zanpakuto is an ice-snow type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.30,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.54,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to, I can \Nmanipulate ice and snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.10,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you make that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.76,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.82,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn’t things be faster \Nif you made it snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:44.46,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,My powers are not meant \Nto show off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:48.05,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, that sounds complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.87,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it’ll snow soon, even \Nwithout me doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.17,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.59,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.78,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be snowing pretty soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.41,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,When it does, let’s \Nmake an even bigger one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.38,B2,YOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.33,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.35,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru…when it snows…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.40,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:19.48,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That is your job, isn’t it, Toshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.96,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what’s best for Yosuke’s \Nhappiness too, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.58,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.66,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been quite a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:53.12,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,but it hasn’t snowed even \Nthough it looks like it might.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.30,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.85,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.80,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.37,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Considering when he became
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.74,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,a spirit and the strength \Nof his obsession,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.54,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn’t be odd at all if \Nhe turned into a Hollow by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.33,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it a good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.33,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,if he doesn’t turn into a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.48,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Granny’s late…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.38,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.33,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.68,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t like the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.88,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe it’s best if I used my
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.41,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto to make it snow, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.44,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Yosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.36,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.02,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.44,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.33,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.02,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.29,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.11,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Her Spiritual Pressure is weakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.00,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.33,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.13,B2,YOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Grand…ma…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.61,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.93,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Was Grandma Haru using her \Nown Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.30,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent Yosuke from transforming…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.43,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,into a Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.26,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.52,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.65,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.66,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.77,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.83,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.70,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Grandma Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.96,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:54.01,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it… Where’d he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.62,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.48,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.91,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:34.73,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.38,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that Yosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.64,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there anything you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.82,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Once he’s become a Hollow…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.48,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,there’s nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.65,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.95,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.04,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be able to see snow soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.41,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on just a little while longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.51,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.37,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.36,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:26.09,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma…Haru…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.56,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.29,B2,HARU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, I know.  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.08,B2,HARU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is your job, isn’t it, Toshiro? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:51.53,B2,HARU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s what’s best for Yosuke’s \Nhappiness too, isn’t it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.08,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.75,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:13.32,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened because \NI wasn’t strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.14,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.01,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.03,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Haru…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.55,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:00.07,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke saw the snow, didn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.68,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.26,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Toshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.75,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:17.72,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro… I’m sorry for \Ncausing you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.86,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not your fault, Grandma Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.64,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.05,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.78,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I started \Ncoming over to visit too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.91,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a small soccer field nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.52,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,so I’ll bring my friends too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.35,B2,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,My, that’ll make things very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.48,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.89,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Yosuke stopped \Nbecause of Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.21,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I think Yosuke was \Nbattling within himself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.54,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,even after he turned into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.52,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why he stopped, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.30,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.54,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m done with my business \Nhere, so I’ll be going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.03,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.06,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Drop by again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.03,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll keep your name on \Nour team’s game roster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.35,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.30,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.27,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I still have leave days left,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:35.55,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I’ll drop by my Grandma’s \Nplace in the Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:22.23,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Karin’s out on a date again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, it’s not like that \Nbetween Karin and Toshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:27.42,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,But I see them going somewhere \Ntogether every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.20,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,That never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:29.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.59,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,You think they’ll get married \Nwhen they’re older?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.34,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:38.72,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:40.13,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.13,0:23:40.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:44.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:46.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you all doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:50.05,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I invited them to celebrate \Nthe new story arc!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I didn’t hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:53.61,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:55.24,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,you probably weren’t paying \Nattention when you heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:57.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:59.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. But I don’t \Nhave anywhere to sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:00.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:03.50,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we’ll be starting a new \Nstory arc beginning next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:04.62,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,